{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CIAYO Comics REWARDS Kembali Dengan Hadiah Yang Lebih Menarik!","content":"\n<p>Siapa yang masih ingat dengan CIAYO Comics REWARDS? Untuk mengingatkan kembali, program ini adalah tempat dimana kamu bisa menjawab pertanyaan seputar CIAYO Comics dan mengumpulkan poin yang bisa ditukar dengan berbagai hadiah menarik. Setelah sebelumnya <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-rehat/\">rehat sejenak </a>di bulan November, kini CIAYO Comics REWARDS kembali lagi!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>CIAYO Comics REWARDS kali ini bakalan beda dengan yang sebelumnya. Yang pasti, kali ini kamu bakal dapat lebih banyak hadiah menarik, lebih banyak poin, dan juga lebih banyak challenge yang menantang! Penasaran apa aja yang beda kali ini?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Yang Baru di CIAYO Comics REWARDS</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Bisa Dapat Poin Lebih Banyak!</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53258\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53258\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di CIAYO Comics REWARDS kali ini, kamu bakal mengumpulkan poin yang disebut dengan Scrolls. Mungkin kamu masih ingat di CIAYO Comics Reward terdahulu, kamu bisa mendapat hingga 50 koin jika bisa menjawab 5 pertanyaan dengan benar (5 koin per jawaban benar). Sekarang, kamu bisa mendapatkan 30 Scrolls jika menjawab dengan benar. Artinya kamu bisa mendapatkan total 150 poin setiap harinya jika bisa menjawab pertanyaan dengan benar!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Hadiah Lebih Menarik!</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53259\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics Rewards\" class=\"wp-image-53259\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Lebih banyak hadiah menanti buat kamu redeem kali ini, dan pastinya cocok banget buat kamu. Apa kamu mahasiswa yang lagi kepepet uang bulanannya? Tenang, karena kamu bisa mendapatkan satu boks Indomie Goreng. Kamu suka olahraga? Ada Xiaomi Mi Band 3. Kalau gamer? Ada Nintendo 2DS dengan bonus game gratis! Hadiahnya keren-keren kan?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Bonus Melimpah Buat Member CIAYO Comics Plus+!</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53260\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53260\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Buat kamu yang udah punya CIAYO Comics Plus+, ada bonus yang gak kalah keren buat kamu. Spesial buat siapapun yang sudah bergabung dengan CIAYO Comics Plus+, kamu bakal mendapatkan bonus 5000 Scrolls secara gratis! Dengan 5000 Scrolls, kamu bisa semakin cepat me-redeem hadiah yang kamu mau!</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Tergiur kan sama hadiah-hadiahnya? Kalau kamu belum tahu cara main CIAYO Comics Rewards, ikuti tahapan sederhana berikut ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cara Main CIAYO Comics REWARDS</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>1. Login/Buat Akun CIAYO Comics</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50702\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/02-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" class=\"wp-image-50702\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tahap pertama sebelum ikut CIAYO Comics REWARDS, kamu harus punya akun CIAYO Comics dulu. Kalau sudah punya, tinggal login saja dengan akun kamu. Kalau belum, buruan bikin! Dengan akun CIAYO Comics, kamu bisa simpan semua subscribe komik kamu dan ikut komentar di komik favorit kamu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu bisa login dan buat akun CIAYO Comics dengan mengklik tombol Login/Register di kanan atas layar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Buka Halaman REWARDS</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53261\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53261\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau sudah login, kamu bisa akses halaman REWARDS di http://rewards.ciayo.com atau dengan mengklik banner CIAYO Comics REWARDS di halaman depan. Di halaman ini, kamu bisa cek jumlah Scrolls kamu dan ikut kuis harian. Untuk cek Scrolls kamu, klik tombol My Scroll di kanan atas layar. Untuk mulai kuis harian, klik tombol Start Today’s Trivia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Jawab 5 Pertanyaan Setiap Harinya</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53262\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53262\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah mengklik tombol Start Today’s Trivia, kamu akan diberikan 5 pertanyaan dengan pilihan ganda. Pertanyaannya nggak serumit Ujian Nasional, kok! Kalau kamu baca komik-komiknya CIAYO Comics, yakin deh semuanya bisa kamu jawab dengan tepat! Cukup klik jawaban yang menurut kamu tepat, dan nanti hasilnya akan muncul.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seperti yang sudah disinggung di atas, setiap pertanyaan yang benar akan mendapatkan 30 Scrolls, dengan total Scrolls maksimal yang bisa kamu dapatkan per harinya adalah 150 Scrolls. Untuk setiap jawaban yang benar, Scrolls yang didapat akan diakumulasikan untuk ditambah ke dalam koleksi Scrolls kamu. Untuk dapat lebih banyak Scrolls, jawab kembali kuisnya besok dan seterusnya sampai kamu mendapatkan Scrolls sebanyak yang kamu mau.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. Tukar Scrolls Dengan Hadiah!</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53263\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"ciayo comics rewards\" class=\"wp-image-53263\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika sudah punya Scrolls cukup, kamu bisa menukar Scrolls dengan mengklik tombol Redeem di sisi atas layar atau di layar hasil kuis. Kamu bisa menukar Scrolls kamu dengan berbagai macam hadiah!</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Jadi tunggu apa lagi? Kapan lagi kamu bisa baca komik dan dapat hadiah di waktu yang bersamaan? Uji pengetahuan kamu tentang CIAYO Comics dan dunia perkomikan di CIAYO Comics Rewards!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d8ab25cb-16e9-52fb-8e8f-44be718c2f0a"}}}